wdi-GC.REV.GOTR.CN.def: Grants and other revenue include grants from other foreign governments, international organizations, and other government units; interest; dividends; rent; requited, nonrepayable receipts for public purposes (such as fines, administrative fees, and entrepreneurial income from government owner­ship of property); and voluntary, unrequited, nonrepayable receipts other than grants.
wdi-GC.REV.GOTR.CN.name: Grants and other revenue
wdi-GC.REV.GOTR.CN.source: International Monetary Fund, Government Finance Statistics Yearbook and data files.
